{"parentUuid":"8ec93b1d-4486-49cb-bc93-baf7ecb63fc9","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"ab5f8963-cf84-4410-bcde-8011a87d1e73","agentId":"a594aec0f6deff72c","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HsGyquJ96WeiL1vHB21JvD","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Mermaid diagram examples\n2\t\n3\tCanonical shapes for `system_architecture.md`. Regenerate only the diagram the\n4\tchange affects.\n5\t\n6\t## Request / data flow (flowchart)\n7\t\n8\t```mermaid\n9\tflowchart LR\n10\t    Client[Browser] -->|HTTPS| API[API service]\n11\t    API -->|require_auth| Auth[Firebase Auth]\n12\t    API -->|read/write| DB[(Orders DB)]\n13\t    API -->|OTLP| Collector[ADOT Collector]\n14\t    Collector --> XRay[AWS X-Ray]\n15\t```\n16\t\n17\t## Auth handshake (sequenceDiagram)\n18\t\n19\t```mermaid\n20\tsequenceDiagram\n21\t    participant U as User\n22\t    participant FE as Frontend\n23\t    participant API as Backend\n24\t    participant FB as Firebase\n25\t    U->>FE: sign in (OAuth)\n26\t    FE->>FB: token exchange\n27\t    FB-->>FE: ID token\n28\t    FE->>API: request + Bearer token\n29\t    API->>API: require_auth -> require_mfa\n30\t    API-->>FE: 200 / 401 / 403\n31\t```\n32\t\n33\t## Data model (erDiagram)\n34\t\n35\t```mermaid\n36\terDiagram\n37\t    USER ||--o{ ORDER : places\n38\t    ORDER ||--|{ ORDER_ITEM : contains\n39\t    USER {\n40\t        string uid\n41\t        string email\n42\t    }\n43\t    ORDER {\n44\t        string id\n45\t        string uid\n46\t        int amount_cents\n47\t    }\n48\t```\n49\t"}]},"uuid":"6eab4cdf-8300-4e17-b1a1-329392629a5f","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:40:10.076Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"8ec93b1d-4486-49cb-bc93-baf7ecb63fc9","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
