{"parentUuid":"417d81cf-7b50-42ba-8097-23361d9fd0f3","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a594aec0f6deff72c","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcqnpKDp1dDtrkKNEoCfs","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01X1NzGz8zALZCBAqVkg6m7Y","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\alembic\\README.md","old_string":"**Schema evolution:**\n- 0001 creates the initial schema (api_keys, events tables).\n- 0002 extends the schema with the usage_rollup derived table and backfills it from events.\n- Future migrations follow the same pattern: version number increments, only forward/backward are specified.","new_string":"**Schema evolution:**\n- 0001 creates the initial schema (api_keys, events tables).\n- 0002 extends the schema with the usage_rollup derived table and backfills it from events.\n- 0003 creates the `quotas` table (per-tenant, per-customer, per-metric usage caps, RLS\n  `FORCE`d so the app-role table owner can't bypass it) and expands `api_keys` with a\n  `scope` column (`'ingest'` default, `'admin'` elevated), both in one expand-only revision.\n- Future migrations follow the same pattern: version number increments, only forward/backward are specified."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2113,"cache_read_input_tokens":84760,"output_tokens":497,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2113},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":497,"cache_read_input_tokens":84760,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2113,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2113,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Ccqnp