{"parentUuid":"1125d9d9-f171-460d-a859-fa3101e359c2","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"ab5f8963-cf84-4410-bcde-8011a87d1e73","agentId":"a594aec0f6deff72c","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BzJz18c3EM7bJKGBG5735y","type":"tool_result","content":"28\t- Human operators call `seed_api_key.py` to provision new API keys (for staging/test/prod as needed).\n29\t\n30\t## Notes\n31\t\n32\t**API key provisioning:**\n33\t- `seed_api_key.py` reads the database connection from `DATABASE_URL` env var (or Secrets Manager if not set).\n34\t- Takes optional CLI args: `--key_id` (public key handle, defaults to generated random), `--label` (human description), `--rate_limit_per_sec` (token bucket limit, defaults to 100).\n35\t- Outputs: the full token `mtr_live_<key_id>_<secret>`, which should be shared with the caller.\n36\t- The script runs in the context of the deployed environment (same database as the app).\n37\t"}]},"uuid":"2af0e873-3f89-4394-a601-ac6b75591001","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:41:59.374Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"1125d9d9-f171-460d-a859-fa3101e359c2","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
