{"parentUuid":"9bb79210-3ed8-43f6-a486-f28ea575b908","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a594aec0f6deff72c","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011Ccqo5N77kWPBB7ThUFQCC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let's add a Mermaid diagram to `docs/system_architecture.md` to satisfy the required diagram type, converting the existing ASCII overview."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":766,"cache_read_input_tokens":102027,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":766,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Ccqo5LnVHZvusofKijWE7","attributionAgent":"documentation","type":"assistant","uuid":"f4ae2ec2-c6fe-4c45-8736-95ebf32782fd","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:44:48.772Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
{"parentUuid":"f4ae2ec2-c6fe-4c45-8736-95ebf32782fd","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a594aec0f6deff72c","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011Ccqo5N77kWPBB7ThUFQCC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WgHxQaAR8aY6gb9WcaxVJf","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\docs\\system_architecture.md","old_string":"```\nClient --HTTPS+API key--> ALB --> FastAPI (ECS Fargate, >=2 tasks)\n                                     |-- Tier-1 (IP) / Tier-2 (api_key_id) throttle --> Redis\n                                     |-- bound-parameter SQL, RLS-scoped -------------> RDS PostgreSQL\n                                     |-- DB credential fetch ------------------------> Secrets Manager\n                                     |-- traces/logs/errors -------------------------> CloudWatch/X-Ray/Sentry\n```","new_string":"```\nClient --HTTPS+API key--> ALB --> FastAPI (ECS Fargate, >=2 tasks)\n                                     |-- Tier-1 (IP) / Tier-2 (api_key_id) throttle --> Redis\n                                     |-- bound-parameter SQL, RLS-scoped -------------> RDS PostgreSQL\n                                     |-- DB credential fetch ------------------------> Secrets Manager\n                                     |-- traces/logs/errors -------------------------> CloudWatch/X-Ray/Sentry\n```\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    Client[Client] -->|\"HTTPS + API key\"| ALB[ALB]\n    ALB --> FastAPI[\"FastAPI (ECS Fargate, >=2 tasks)\"]\n    FastAPI -->|\"Tier-1 IP+route / Tier-2 api_key_id throttle\"| Redis[(Redis)]\n    FastAPI -->|\"require_api_key: cache hit or Argon2id verify\"| AuthDB[(RDS PostgreSQL: api_keys)]\n    FastAPI -->|\"POST /v1/events: insert + quota check + rollup upsert\"| EventsDB[(RDS PostgreSQL: events / usage_rollup / quotas)]\n    FastAPI -->|\"GET /v1/usage: read rollup\"| EventsDB\n    FastAPI -->|\"PUT /v1/quotas: upsert cap\"| EventsDB\n    FastAPI -->|\"DB credential fetch\"| Secrets[Secrets Manager]\n    FastAPI -->|\"traces/logs/errors\"| Observability[\"CloudWatch / X-Ray / Sentry\"]\n```"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":766,"cache_read_input_tokens":102027,"output_tokens":989,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":766},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":989,"cache_read_input_tokens":102027,"cache_creation_input_tokens":766,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":766,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Ccqo5LnVHZvusofKijWE7","attributionAgent":"documentation","type":"assistant","uuid":"323b92b3-214e-4ea8-8668-6324f1b0bfe2","timestamp":"2026-07-09T03:44:55.186Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"d6fd840f-4c15-4ec4-8e2b-f4a42b2cbb1a","version":"2.1.204","gitBranch":"feature/metric-quotas"}
